snippet.title: Pretend Cars Racing - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Pretend Cars Racing is an old-school top down racer, with 13 tracks, 4 car classes, AI, split-screen and head to head racing.
You can play it at http://misterakuma.itch.io

The music in the trailer is We Love Punk Rock by WinnieTheMoog
Link: https://filmmusic.io/song/6369-we-love-punk-rock
License: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
